  <brief_title>Evaluating the Effectiveness of Point-of-care Diagnostic Technologies in MCH Services in Mozambique</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluating the Effectiveness of Point-of-care Diagnostic Technologies in MCH Services and Their Impact on Mother and Child Health Outcomes in Cabo Delgado Province, Mozambique</official_title>
